922
01:10:31,395 --> 01:10:33,314
我没有。这是我爸爸的。
I don't have one. It's my dad's.

923
01:10:41,447 --> 01:10:42,531
米奇!
Mitch!

924
01:10:51,332 --> 01:10:53,834
————什么?——嘿!最近怎么样，杰瑞?
- What the--? - Hey! How's it going, Jerry?

925
01:10:55,044 --> 01:10:56,629
你想要什么，奈特?
What do you want, Knight?

926
01:10:56,712 --> 01:11:00,007
世界和平。但我觉得现在不是讨论这个的时候。
World peace. But I don't think this is the time to discuss it.

927
01:11:00,090 --> 01:11:03,260
——出去!-你可能会感兴趣，杰瑞。
- Get out! - Something might interest you, Jerry.

928
01:11:03,344 --> 01:11:07,723
-你说什么我都不感兴趣。-海瑟薇博士…苏珊。
- I'm not interested in anything you say. - Dr. Hathaway... Susan.

929
01:11:15,773 --> 01:11:17,483
我解决了电力问题，杰瑞。
I solved the power problem, Jerry.

930
01:11:20,903 --> 01:11:22,279
杰里?
Jerry?

931
01:11:22,363 --> 01:11:23,364
乘出租车。
Take a cab.

932
01:11:25,032 --> 01:11:26,951
所以你以后再敲。
So you'll hammer later.

933
01:11:33,540 --> 01:11:36,877
你也知道，米奇和我在研究氰化物系统。
As you know, Mitch and I were working on the cyanide system.

934
01:11:36,961 --> 01:11:40,381
今天早些时候，它把自己吃掉了。
Well, earlier today, it ate itself.

935
01:11:41,215 --> 01:11:45,886
但这正是我们向前迈出一大步所需要的。
But that's just what we needed to take a giant step forward.

936
01:11:45,970 --> 01:11:46,971
肯特?
Right, Kent?

937
01:11:48,472 --> 01:11:52,017
不用说，我对熔毁的事有点沮丧。
Needless to say, I was a little despondent about the meltdown.

938
01:11:52,101 --> 01:11:57,022
但就在我准备哈利卡里的时候，我突然想到了。
But then, in the midst of my preparations for hari-kari, it came to me.

939
01:11:58,107 --> 01:12:02,569
在氩基体中合成激发态溴是可能的。
It is possible to synthesize excited bromide in an argon matrix.

940
01:12:02,653 --> 01:12:06,031
是的。它是一个处于激发态的准分子。
Yes. It's an excimer, frozen in its excited state.

941
01:12:06,115 --> 01:12:07,825
这是不可能的。
That's impossible.

942
01:12:07,908 --> 01:12:10,744
这是化学激光器。但是是固态的，不是气态的。
It's a chemical laser. But in solid, not gaseous form.

943
01:12:11,537 --> 01:12:16,625
简而言之，为了尊重你，肯特，这就像发射一根炸药。
Put simply, in deference to you, Kent, it's like lasing a stick of dynamite.

944
01:12:16,709 --> 01:12:22,381
只要我们施加一个场，我们就耦合到一个与地面辐射耦合的状态。
As soon as we apply a field, we couple to a state that is radiatively coupled to the ground.

945
01:12:22,965 --> 01:12:33,809
