This is a complete waste of time.

952
01:12:55,497 --> 01:12:58,792
肯特，帮我个忙，把靶子放在煤渣砖前面，好吗?
Do me a favor, Kent, put the target in front of the cinder blocks, will you?

953
01:13:08,135 --> 01:13:10,345
好的，到防护罩后面来。
Okay, come behind the shield.

954
01:13:19,313 --> 01:13:22,691
-好的，泰勒先生。-随时准备好。
- Okay, Mr. Taylor. - Any time you're ready.

955
01:13:24,151 --> 01:13:25,152
好的。
Okay.

956
01:13:26,028 --> 01:13:27,029
准备好了吗?
Ready?

957
01:13:27,696 --> 01:13:28,822
激光!
Laser on!

958
01:13:31,658 --> 01:13:33,118
哇!
Whoa!

959
01:13:35,204 --> 01:13:37,581
——太棒了!——好吧!
- Fantastic! - All right!

960
01:13:41,376 --> 01:13:42,377
看看这个!
Look at this!

961
01:13:47,299 --> 01:13:48,509
哇。
Wow.

962
01:13:51,929 --> 01:13:55,224
-对不起，窗户坏了，先生。-还有院子对面的树!
- Sorry about the window, sir. - And the trees across the quad!

963
01:13:55,307 --> 01:13:56,809
-多好的团队啊!——是的!
- What a team! - Yeah!

964
01:14:00,145 --> 01:14:03,357
-你做到了。-我也做了我该做的。
- You did it. - I did my part too.

965
01:14:03,941 --> 01:14:06,318
你毕业。你得到了这份工作。
You graduate. You get the job.

966
01:14:06,902 --> 01:14:09,905
什么? !你不能!那是我的工作。
What?! You can't! That's my job.

967
01:14:10,697 --> 01:14:14,576
你让我做的我都做了。你不能这么做!
I've done everything you've ever asked me to. You can't do this!

968
01:14:14,660 --> 01:14:16,203
看!看!
Look! Look!

969
01:14:16,286 --> 01:14:17,996
