- Am I gonna meet your parents? - No.

989
01:15:34,656 --> 01:15:38,619
——为什么?你为我感到羞耻吗?——不,他们!
- Why? Are you ashamed of me? - No, them!

990
01:15:38,702 --> 01:15:39,870
哦!
Oh!

991
01:15:39,953 --> 01:15:42,497
你最好记住该感谢的人。
You better remember the right people to thank on this.

992
01:15:42,581 --> 01:15:45,709
——听好了。我要感谢我的鱼。-什么意思?
- Listen up. I'd like to thank my fish. - What do you mean?

993
01:15:45,792 --> 01:15:47,794
-还有Ikagami先生!-哦，我喜欢。
- And Mr. Ikagami! - Oh, I love it.

994
01:15:47,878 --> 01:15:49,296
不，我说的是…
No, what I was talking about...

995
01:15:52,925 --> 01:15:55,719
