- It's, uh... - What are you trying to say?

996
01:15:55,802 --> 01:15:56,970
Lazlo。
Lazlo.

997
01:16:07,606 --> 01:16:10,776
拉兹洛，我很高兴你出来了。你要一个汉堡包吗?
Lazlo, I'm so glad you came out. You want a hamburger?

998
01:16:10,859 --> 01:16:12,986
我一直在考虑你的激光方案。
I've been thinking about your laser solution.

999
01:16:13,070 --> 01:16:14,071
哦,很好。
Oh, good.

1000
01:16:14,655 --> 01:16:18,408
我想你已经把输出功率增加到6兆瓦了。
I figure you've increased the power output to 6 megawatts.

1001
01:16:18,492 --> 01:16:19,910
是的,。
Yeah, about that.

1002
01:16:20,994 --> 01:16:23,956
-你用它做什么?-做巨大的瑞士奶酪?
- What would you use that for? - Making enormous Swiss cheese?

1003
01:16:25,415 --> 01:16:27,042
应用是无限的。
The applications are unlimited.

1004
01:16:27,125 --> 01:16:31,630
不。用你想出来的燃料，光束能维持多久，15秒吧?
No. With the fuel you've come up with, the beam would last for what, 15 seconds?

1005
01:16:31,713 --> 01:16:34,800
-那有什么用?-拉兹洛，那不重要
- What good is that? - Oh, Lazlo, that doesn't matter.

1006
01:16:34,883 --> 01:16:36,593
我尊重你，但我已经毕业了。
I respect you, but I graduated.

1007
01:16:36,677 --> 01:16:40,055
让工程师们想办法利用它。这不关我们的事。
Let the engineers figure out a use for it. That's not our concern.

1008
01:16:40,138 --> 01:16:45,143
也许有人已经有了它的用途，它是专门为它设计的。
Maybe somebody already has a use for it, one for which it is specifically designed.

1009
01:16:45,227 --> 01:16:48,105
海瑟薇博士一直在想什么?
Dr. Hathaway had something in mind all along?

1010
01:16:48,188 --> 01:16:50,023
看看事实吧。
Look at the facts.

1011
01:16:50,107 --> 01:16:55,946
功率非常高，携带方便，发射时间有限，射程无限。
Very high power, portable, limited firing time, unlimited range.

1012
01:16:56,029 --> 01:17:02,286
你只需要一个跟踪系统和一个大旋转镜，你就可以从太空蒸发一个人类目标。
All you need is a tracking system and a large spinning mirror, and you could vaporize a human target from space.

1013
01:17:05,038 --> 01:17:06,206
这并不好。
This is not good.

1014
01:17:14,715 --> 01:17:15,716
不。
No.

1015
01:17:16,550 --> 01:17:17,634
发生了什么事?
What happened?

1016
01:17:22,306 --> 01:17:23,390
哦,不。
Oh, no.

1017
01:17:25,517 --> 01:17:26,852
——克里斯。-我没事。
- Chris. - I'm all right.

1018
01:17:32,899 --> 01:17:36,028
-他们拿走了一切。-肯特的追踪系统没了!
- They took everything. - Kent's tracking system's gone!

1019
01:17:39,031 --> 01:17:40,991
你怎么能造出那面镜子!
How could you build that mirror?!

1020
01:17:50,417 --> 01:17:51,501
他骗了我们。
He lied to us.

1021
01:17:53,253 --> 01:17:55,088
骗你很容易，米奇。
It's easy to lie to you, Mitch.

1022
01:17:57,215 --> 01:17:58,675
你信任的人。
You trust people.

1023
01:17:59,301 --> 01:18:00,427
我是一个愤世嫉俗者。
I'm a cynic.

1024
01:18:03,638 --> 01:18:04,848
我真是个混蛋。
I'm such an asshole.

1025
01:18:05,640 --> 01:18:09,019
我理解你的感受，克里斯。你是对的。
I understand how you feel, Chris. And you're right.

1026
01:18:10,062 --> 01:18:12,939
但我们现在应该做的是找出他在做什么。
But what we should be doing now is finding out what he's doing.

1027
01:18:13,690 --> 01:18:14,691
肯特。
Kent.

1028
01:18:21,948 --> 01:18:23,492
嘘!你们。
Shh! You guys.

1029
01:18:44,054 --> 01:18:47,182
-我们有两分钟时间。两分钟。——原谅?
- We'll have two minutes. Two minutes. - Pardon?

1030
01:18:53,271 --> 01:18:55,524
-嗨。-嗨。
- Hi. - Hi.

1031
01:19:14,584 --> 01:19:15,836
好了，张开他的嘴。
Okay, open his mouth.

1032
01:19:18,672 --> 01:19:19,923
好的。斗牛犬。
Okay. Bulldogs.

1033
01:19:22,259 --> 01:19:23,301
和收发器。
And transceiver.

1034
01:19:24,511 --> 01:19:25,637
和镊子。
And tweezers.

1035
01:19:28,765 --> 01:19:31,518
是牙套给了我灵感。
See, it was the braces that gave me the idea.

1036
01:19:31,601 --> 01:19:34,855
它们是完美的天线。他的整个脑袋变成了一个说话的人。
They're a perfect antennae. His whole head becomes a speaker.

1037
01:19:34,938 --> 01:19:37,107
是时候有人好好利用它了。
It's about time someone put it to good use.

1038
01:19:44,906 --> 01:19:45,907
肯特?
Kent?

1039
01:19:47,617 --> 01:19:50,495
肯特。醒来,肯特。
Kent. Wake up, Kent.

1040
01:19:54,291 --> 01:19:55,125
噢!
Ow!

1041
01:19:55,208 --> 01:19:56,376
-肯特!——什么?
- Kent! - What?

1042
01:19:56,460 --> 01:19:58,545
我在跟你说话，肯特。
I'm talking to you, Kent.

1043
01:20:00,380 --> 01:20:04,301
-这是什么?-我说了，我在和你说话。
- What is this? - I said, I'm talking to you.

1044
01:20:04,384 --> 01:20:06,219
——没有。-是的。
- No. - Yeah.

1045
01:20:08,346 --> 01:20:10,432
我没睡着。
Well, I'm not asleep.

1046
01:20:11,933 --> 01:20:15,187
-我一定是工作过度了。-你没有过度劳累，肯特。
- I must be overworked. - You're not overworked, Kent.

1047
01:20:16,104 --> 01:20:17,564
我又没疯!
Well, I'm not insane!

1048
01:20:20,650 --> 01:20:23,612
-我有吗?-那还有待观察，肯特
- Or am I? - That remains to be seen, Kent.

1049
01:20:23,695 --> 01:20:25,864
但我们正在谈话。
But we are having a conversation.

1050
01:20:30,869 --> 01:20:34,581
-你是谁?-这是耶稣，肯特。
- Okay, who is this? - This is Jesus, Kent.

1051
01:20:34,664 --> 01:20:38,251
你是一个非常淘气的孩子!
And you've been a very naughty boy!

1052
01:20:40,420 --> 01:20:43,757
好吧，你是谁?
All right, who is this?

1053
01:20:43,840 --> 01:20:47,219
-少废话，肯特你造了个武器。——什么?
- Cut the crap, Kent. You built a weapon. - What?

1054
01:20:47,302 --> 01:20:52,057
你以为秘密相位共轭跟踪系统是干什么用的?
What do you think a secret phase-conjugate tracking system is for?

1055
01:20:53,141 --> 01:20:56,269
大镜子形成大光束。
A big mirror makes a big beam.

1056
01:21:00,273 --> 01:21:01,525
我想可能是吧。
I guess it could be.

1057
01:21:02,484 --> 01:21:04,319
激光现在在哪里?
Where's the laser now?

1058
01:21:05,570 --> 01:21:11,451
我无意中听到杰瑞提到27号有个考试。
I overheard Jerry mention something about a test on the 27th.

1059
01:21:12,244 --> 01:21:14,037
但我不知道在哪里。这是机密。
But I don't know where. It's classified.

1060
01:21:17,916 --> 01:21:20,919
- - - - - -什么? !-哦，呃，没什么。
- What?! - Oh, uh, nothing.

1061
01:21:21,670 --> 01:21:25,257
我要你想想你做了什么，肯特。
I want you to think about what you've done, Kent.

1062
01:21:26,132 --> 01:21:30,095
从现在开始，别跟自己玩了!
And from now on, stop playing with yourself!

1063
01:21:35,308 --> 01:21:36,601
它是上帝。
It is God.

1064
01:21:37,352 --> 01:21:38,436
现在怎么办呢?
Now what?

1065
01:21:42,732 --> 01:21:43,942
第二阶段。
Phase two.

1066
01:21:46,403 --> 01:21:47,946
你是怎么回事?!
What is it with you?!

1067
01:23:30,674 --> 01:23:31,675
那是什么?
What's that?

1068
01:23:32,592 --> 01:23:37,138
-这些军人太不信任人了。-我们不能进入基地?
- These military people are so untrusting. - We can't get on-base clearance?

1069
01:23:37,222 --> 01:23:40,016
——我们将。-只需要6个小时
- We will. - It's just gonna take six hours.

1070
01:23:40,100 --> 01:23:42,185
算了吧。我们将球。
Forget it. We'll balls it.

1071
01:23:42,268 --> 01:23:43,436
这些看起来怎么样?
How do these look?

1072
01:23:45,355 --> 01:23:47,816
糟透了。我的像他，他的像我。
Terrible. Mine looks like him, and his looks like me.

1073
01:23:49,693 --> 01:23:50,694
太好了,我希望。
Great, I hope.

1074
01:23:50,777 --> 01:23:53,738
-如果这些骗不了任何人呢?-他们向我们开枪。
- What if these don't fool anybody? - They shoot us.

1075
01:23:59,160 --> 01:24:00,161
ID吗?
ID?

1076
01:24:04,541 --> 01:24:07,043
-把这些给下一个门的警卫看。——好的。你的赌注。
- Show these to the guard at the next gate. - Okey-doke. You bet.

1077
01:24:19,764 --> 01:24:21,182
id吗?
IDs?

1078
01:24:21,266 --> 01:24:23,059
嘿，你能把它收起来吗，伙计?我们刚飞过来。
Hey, can you snap it up, buddy? We just flew in.

1079
01:24:23,143 --> 01:24:27,063
我们迟到了，又累又饿，还租了辆破车。
We're late, we're tired, we're hungry, we rented this stupid car.

1080
01:24:27,147 --> 01:24:30,775
-你疯了吗?-你得恐吓他们。很酷。
- Are you out of your mind? - You gotta intimidate these guys. Be cool.

1081
01:24:31,985 --> 01:24:33,027
你不在名单上。
You're not on the list.

1082
01:24:33,945 --> 01:24:37,240
单吗?不在名单上。是啊，因为我们是机密。
List? Not on the list. Yeah, that's because we're classified.

1083
01:24:37,323 --> 01:24:38,324
是的。
Yeah.

1084
01:24:40,285 --> 01:24:41,286
安全。
Security.

1085
01:24:42,620 --> 01:24:43,705
是的,先生。
Yes, sir.

1086
01:24:43,788 --> 01:24:46,332
你们做技术员是不是太年轻了?
Aren't you guys a little young to be technicians?

1087
01:24:46,416 --> 01:24:48,042
激光是一门年轻的科学。
Lasers are a young science.

1088
01:24:48,752 --> 01:24:52,422
好的。好吧，是你逼我说的。现在我们都有麻烦了。
Okay. There, fine, you made me say it. Now we're both in trouble.

1089
01:24:52,505 --> 01:24:54,340
听着，我会打电话给值班警官。
Look, I'll call the duty officer.

1090
01:24:54,924 --> 01:24:57,635
——嗯…-你好，空降兵。
- Uh... - Hey there, uh, Airborne.

1091
01:25:02,140 --> 01:25:03,224
不要这样做。
Don't do that.

1092
01:25:03,308 --> 01:25:06,436
如果你打了电话，那就是我们的工作了。我们晚了四个小时。
If you make that call, it's our jobs. We're four hours late.

1093
01:25:06,519 --> 01:25:09,689
-是的，先生-让我们休息一下，好吗?
- Yes, sir. - Give us a break, will you, buddy?

1094
01:25:09,773 --> 01:25:12,358
也许有一天你也会在私营部门工作，对吧?
Someday you might be in the private sector too, right?

1095
01:25:12,442 --> 01:25:13,443
是的。
Yeah.

1096
01:25:16,321 --> 01:25:17,322
是的。
Yes.

1097
01:25:18,948 --> 01:25:21,409
——我们死了。-哦,不。
- We're dead. - Oh, no.

1098
01:25:23,953 --> 01:25:25,079
是的,先生。
Yes, sir.

1099
01:25:25,163 --> 01:25:26,915
——好的。-我喜欢。
- All right. - I love it.

1100
01:25:29,042 --> 01:25:30,168
当然,先生。
Absolutely, sir.

1101
01:25:30,919 --> 01:25:32,212
把它完成了。
Consider it done.

1102
01:25:33,087 --> 01:25:34,088
是的,先生。
Yes, sir.

1103
01:25:36,966 --> 01:25:40,220
-寻找任何不寻常的东西。——好的。
- Look for anything out of the ordinary. - Okay.

1104
01:25:42,722 --> 01:25:44,599
米奇。米奇,过来。
Mitch. Mitch, come here.

1105
01:25:46,768 --> 01:25:48,102
我的上帝。
My God.

1106
01:25:51,898 --> 01:25:52,982
好吧,来吧。
Okay, come on.

1107
01:26:06,329 --> 01:26:07,914
——板载内存?——检查。
- Onboard RAM? - Check.

1108
01:26:07,997 --> 01:26:10,083
-加载点处理器?——检查。
- Loading point processor? - Check.

1109
01:26:10,166 --> 01:26:11,793
DMA通道。
DMA channel.

1110
01:26:11,876 --> 01:26:13,211
激光控制系统。
Laser control system.

1111
01:26:13,294 --> 01:26:16,214
一级和二级激光探测系统全部启动。
Primary and secondary laser detection systems all go.

1112
01:26:16,297 --> 01:26:19,217
初级和次级激光激活系统全部启动。
Primary and secondary laser activation systems all go.

1113
01:26:19,300 --> 01:26:20,844
——处理器吗?——检查。
- Processor A? - Check.

1114
01:26:20,927 --> 01:26:22,345
- B处理器?——检查。
- Processor B? - Check.

1115
01:26:22,428 --> 01:26:24,055
——通信链路?——开放。
- Communications link? - Open.

1116
01:26:24,681 --> 01:26:27,684
-所有的诊断似乎都没问题。-最后的检查准备好了。
- All the diagnostics seem okay. - Final check ready.

1117
01:26:27,767 --> 01:26:29,269
65度，19分钟。
Sixty-five degrees, 19 minutes.

1118
01:26:29,352 --> 01:26:31,604
经度44度零9分。
Longitude 44 degrees, zero, 9 minutes.

1119
01:26:38,111 --> 01:26:40,780
-所有系统准备。-我们结束了，伙计们
- All systems go. - We're finished here, fellas.

1120
01:26:48,121 --> 01:26:49,497
什么? !
What?!

1121
01:27:18,943 --> 01:27:22,906
这个小多项式会让电脑忙到不知道我们在这里。
This little polynomial should keep the computer so busy, it doesn't even know we're here.

1122
01:27:26,576 --> 01:27:27,869
他们在哪儿?
Where are they?

1123
01:27:32,540 --> 01:27:35,251
-有联系。他们在!——哦!
- Got a connection. They're in! - Oh!

1124
01:27:44,260 --> 01:27:45,428
阿博特科斯特洛。
Abbott to Costello.

1125
01:27:45,511 --> 01:27:47,430
-我是科斯特洛。去做吧。-我们有好东西。
- This is Costello. Go ahead. - We've got the goodies.

1126
01:27:47,513 --> 01:27:50,808
我们已经计算出了目标坐标来进行轨迹调整。
We've got the target coordinates computed for trajectory adjustment.

1127
01:27:51,726 --> 01:27:53,853
收到，我们正在发送
Roger, we're sending.

1128
01:27:59,901 --> 01:28:01,152
——哦。——哦。
- Uh-oh. - Uh-oh.

1129
01:28:01,235 --> 01:28:02,278
它是什么?
What is it?

1130
01:28:05,907 --> 01:28:06,991
哦,没什么。
Oh, nothing.

1131
01:28:10,495 --> 01:28:13,539
你没想过我们会花这么多钱去太空测试吗?
You didn't think we'd blow all this money to test in space?

1132
01:28:13,623 --> 01:28:18,378
事实上，是的，我做了，因为这就是设计的目的。
Actually, yes, I did, because that is what it is designed for.

1133
01:28:18,461 --> 01:28:25,343
但如果以你的智慧，你觉得我们应该先学爬再学走，我是说，那也没关系。真的。
But if, in your wisdom, you feel we should learn to crawl before we walk, I mean, that's fine too. Really.

1134
01:28:26,427 --> 01:28:28,221
——注意!——什么?
- Attention! - What?

1135
01:28:28,304 --> 01:28:31,557
-上级长官来了!-就像你一样。
- Superior officer in the room! - As you were.

1136
01:28:31,641 --> 01:28:35,269
打扰一下。我们准备好进行最后的机载激光检查了。
Excuse me. We're ready for the final onboard laser check.

1137
01:28:35,353 --> 01:28:37,355
嘘!
Shh!

1138
01:28:47,615 --> 01:28:48,616
所有清晰。
All clear.

1139
01:28:49,242 --> 01:28:51,786
我要把PROM换成EPROM。
I'm replacing the PROM with our EPROM.

1140
01:28:57,834 --> 01:28:58,835
好吧,开枪。
Okay, shoot.

1141
01:29:04,716 --> 01:29:06,259
请告诉我坐标好吗?
May I have the coordinates, please?

1142
01:29:08,761 --> 01:29:13,766
北纬34度10分15秒21。
Thirty-four degrees, ten minutes, 15.21 seconds north.

1143
01:29:14,559 --> 01:29:18,563
190度，7分钟……
One hundred nineteen degrees, seven minutes...

1144
01:29:24,152 --> 01:29:25,361
这边走。
Right over this way.

1145
01:29:28,531 --> 01:29:29,866
我去检查楼梯。
I'm gonna check the stairs.

1146
01:29:42,879 --> 01:29:44,505
克里斯!海瑟薇的来了!
Chris! Hathaway's coming!

1147
01:29:44,589 --> 01:29:48,676
米奇刚刚通知我教授先生要来了。
Mitch has just informed me that Herr Professor is approaching.

1148
01:29:48,760 --> 01:29:51,763
-我们该怎么办?!-请快点。海瑟薇的到来。
- What do we do?! - Please hurry. Hathaway's coming.

1149
01:29:51,846 --> 01:29:54,057
请不要。我在压力下工作不好。
Please don't. I don't work well under pressure.

1150
01:29:57,435 --> 01:29:58,770
小心你的头。
Watch your head there.

1151
01:30:05,109 --> 01:30:06,486
我希望这样可以。
I hope that does it.

1152
01:30:06,569 --> 01:30:09,739
好吧，克里斯，我是说艾伯特。喂?喂?
Okay, Chris, I mean, Abbott. Hello? Hello?

1153
01:30:10,907 --> 01:30:12,075
他们跑了!
They're gone!

1154
01:30:12,950 --> 01:30:15,578
——好的。好吧。好吧。——好的。好吧。很好。
- Okay. Fine. Fine. - All right. Fine. Fine.

1155
01:30:17,205 --> 01:30:21,042
戈伊医生会为你解答你可能有的其他问题。
Dr. Goy here will explain any additional questions you might have.

1156
01:30:21,125 --> 01:30:24,378
是的。重复使用这个武器有什么问题吗?
Yes. Is there any problem with reusing the weapon?

1157
01:30:24,462 --> 01:30:25,755
不,没有问题。
No, no problem.

1158
01:30:25,838 --> 01:30:31,344
燃料被冷冻并包含在一个自给自足的单元中——每次使用后都是可更换的。——我明白了。
The fuel is frozen and contained within a self-sufficient unit - that's replaceable after each use. - I see.

1159
01:30:31,427 --> 01:30:38,434
这个系统的美妙之处在于燃料激光器…-这里一切都好吗?-为什么不呢?
The beauty of this system is that the fuel laser... - Is everything all right here? - Why shouldn't it be?

1160
01:30:42,480 --> 01:30:45,691
只要它还有效，我们就去。很好。
As long as it remains operative, we're going. Fine.

1161
01:30:45,775 --> 01:30:50,613
好吧，我想这差不多就是总结了。你不?嗯…我们该走了吗?
Well, I think that just about sums it up. Don't you? Uh... Shall we take our exit?

1162
01:30:51,739 --> 01:30:53,032
在我看来很小。
Looks small to me.

1163
01:30:59,205 --> 01:31:01,958
-好了，他们走了。-好险啊。
- Okay, they're gone. - That was close.

1164
01:31:02,667 --> 01:31:04,877
没有比借B-1更好的了，对吧，将军?
Nothing like borrowing a B-1, huh, general?

1165
01:31:13,469 --> 01:31:14,804
它是什么?
What is it?

1166
01:31:15,888 --> 01:31:16,889
什么都没有。
Nothing.

1167
01:31:23,354 --> 01:31:27,233
客观个人分析诊断精神分裂症…
Diagnosis of schizophrenia by objective personal analysis...

1168
01:31:29,986 --> 01:31:32,530
——嗨,肯特。——哦。
- Hi, Kent. - Oh.

1169
01:31:34,407 --> 01:31:35,783
我以为你已经走了。
I thought you'd gone.

1170
01:31:36,325 --> 01:31:40,079
还没有。你一直在摸自己吗?
Not yet. Have you been touching yourself?

1171
01:31:40,163 --> 01:31:43,166
是的。我的意思是,不!
Yes. I mean, no!

1172
01:31:44,250 --> 01:31:46,502
很好。听着,肯特。
Good. Listen, Kent.

1173
01:31:47,044 --> 01:31:51,757
爸爸，我爸爸，上帝，想给你看样东西。
Dad, you know, my father, God, wants to show you something.

1174
01:31:51,841 --> 01:31:54,427
为什么?我的意思是,什么?
Why? I meant, what?

1175
01:31:54,510 --> 01:31:56,596
我已经学会了不问。
I've learned not to ask.

1176
01:31:57,722 --> 01:32:06,981
他要你今天早上7点08分准时在艾维冠大道639号海瑟薇医生家门口等他。
He wants you to wait in front of Dr. Hathaway's house at 639 Ivy Crest Drive at precisely 7:08 this morning.

1177
01:32:09,400 --> 01:32:10,401
艾薇顶吗?
Ivy Crest?

1178
01:32:10,484 --> 01:32:13,362
就在那儿等着，你会收到信号的。
Just wait there and you shall receive a sign.

1179
01:32:13,446 --> 01:32:15,990
不要绝望，不要走进去。
Do not despair and do not go inside.

1180
01:32:16,073 --> 01:32:17,325
好吧,为什么不呢?
Well, why not?

1181
01:32:21,120 --> 01:32:22,121
喂?
Hello?

1182
01:32:23,748 --> 01:32:25,249
你好,耶稣吗?
Hello, Jesus?

1183
01:32:29,921 --> 01:32:30,922
他挂了电话。
He hung up.

1184
01:32:47,230 --> 01:32:51,025
弓弩一号，雷达发现，航向0-2-5。
Crossbow One, radar contact, take up a heading of 0-2-5.

1185
01:32:51,108 --> 01:32:54,153
爬升到飞行高度6-5-0。
Climb to maintain flight level 6-5-0.

1186
01:32:55,404 --> 01:33:00,618
收到。0-2-5，高度5000，飞行高度6-5-0。
Roger. We are 0-2-5 at a 5000 for flight level 6-5-0.

1187
01:33:25,393 --> 01:33:26,394
他们在这里。
They're here.

1188
01:33:30,856 --> 01:33:36,237
啊。奈特先生，为什么在这里见到你我一点都不惊讶?
Ah. Mr. Knight, why is it that I am not surprised to see you here?

1189
01:33:37,071 --> 01:33:43,369
我想你对我们将要见证的所谓事件有个解释吧。
And, uh, I suppose you have an explanation for this so-called event that we're to witness.

1190
01:33:43,452 --> 01:33:48,457
是的，先生，我知道。但首先，我要称赞你的时尚品味。
Yes, sir, I do. But first, let me compliment you on your fashion sense.

1191
01:33:48,541 --> 01:33:49,959
特别是你的拖鞋。
Particularly your slippers.

1192
01:33:52,586 --> 01:33:55,715
是啊，菲莱米娜喜欢。
Yes, well, uh, Fillamina likes them.

1193
01:33:56,424 --> 01:33:57,425
嘿,伙计们!
Hey, guys!

1194
01:33:58,134 --> 01:34:00,303
——克里斯。——早上好。
- Chris. - Good morning.

1195
01:34:03,097 --> 01:34:06,559
啊。国会议员Doogan。什么风把你吹来了?
Ah. Congressman Doogan. What brings you around?

1196
01:34:06,642 --> 01:34:11,230
我听说这里发生了一件非常重要的国际事件。
I was told there was a situation here of critical international importance.

1197
01:34:18,195 --> 01:34:23,075
所有武器功能都由这个模块控制，就像在太空中一样。
All weapon functions are controlled from this module, as it would be in space.

1198
01:34:23,159 --> 01:34:26,537
事实上，这是一模一样的汽车座舱。
In fact, this is an exact duplicate of the vehicle cockpit.

1199
01:34:26,620 --> 01:34:28,956
精度和功率将是精确的。
The accuracy and the power will be as exact.

1200
01:34:29,040 --> 01:34:32,460
-我们接近目标了。-开门。
- We are nearing the target. - Open the doors.

1201
01:34:32,543 --> 01:34:34,670
弩，打开炸弹舱门。
Crossbow, open bomb bay doors.

1202
01:34:43,179 --> 01:34:46,891
-那是非常严重的指控。-是的，先生，我知道
- Those are very serious accusations. - Yes, sir. I know.

1203
01:34:46,974 --> 01:34:49,310
如果是真的，我需要证据。
If it's true, I'm going to need proof.

1204
01:34:51,020 --> 01:34:53,898
我想我们可以在一分钟内给你们安排时间。
I think we can accommodate you both in just one minute.

1205
01:34:54,440 --> 01:34:55,441
鸭子。
Duck.

1206
01:34:58,194 --> 01:34:59,862
-哦，先生，下来。——国会议员?
- Oh, sir, down. - Congressman?

1207
01:35:42,571 --> 01:35:44,407
现在，你听我说，耶稣。
Now, you listen to me, Jesus.

1208
01:35:46,492 --> 01:35:50,246
这是杰瑞的房子…我们非常接近。
This is Jerry's house... and we're very close.

1209
01:35:51,497 --> 01:35:54,250
如果你不回答我，我就只能进去了。
So if you don't answer me, I'm just gonna have to go in.

1210
01:35:58,796 --> 01:36:01,215
-所以我要走了。——不,肯特!
- So I'm going. - No, Kent!

1211
01:36:01,298 --> 01:36:04,593
——离开!肯特!-别进去!
- Get away! Kent! - Don't go in there!

1212
01:36:04,677 --> 01:36:06,512
快离开那里!
Get away from there!

1213
01:36:06,595 --> 01:36:08,973
-别进去!-肯特!不!
- Don't go in there! - Kent! No!

1214
01:36:09,056 --> 01:36:10,141
肯特!
Kent!

1215
01:36:10,766 --> 01:36:13,102
目标锁定。十。
Target locked. In ten.

1216
01:36:14,645 --> 01:36:15,646
九个
Nine.

1217
01:36:17,189 --> 01:36:18,190
八个
Eight.

1218
01:36:23,612 --> 01:36:26,907
-肯特!-出来，肯特!
- Kent! - Come out, Kent!

1219
01:36:39,044 --> 01:36:43,257
好吧,上帝!给我吧!
Okay, God! Let me have it!

1220
01:36:47,219 --> 01:36:48,846
噢,瞧!
Oh, look!

1221
01:37:28,260 --> 01:37:29,261
爆米花。
Popcorn.

1222
01:37:35,726 --> 01:37:36,727
哦。
Oh.

1223
01:37:48,322 --> 01:37:51,158
不。
No.

1224
01:37:51,992 --> 01:37:54,036
我不明白你的意思。火吗?
I don't understand. Did it fire?

1225
01:37:54,119 --> 01:37:56,830
-开火了吗?-是的，但有个问题。
- Did it fire? - Yes, but there's a problem.

1226
01:37:56,914 --> 01:38:00,584
-它没有关闭。是的。-那就关掉它!
- It's not shutting down. Yes. - Well, shut it down!

1227
01:38:00,668 --> 01:38:03,629
-杰瑞，有什么问题吗?-关掉它!
- Jerry, what's the problem? - Shut it down!

1228
01:38:04,880 --> 01:38:05,881
肯特。
Kent.

1229
01:38:10,135 --> 01:38:11,345
哟!
Whee!

1230
01:38:26,402 --> 01:38:27,945
——啊!-肯特。
- Whee! - Kent.

1231
01:38:28,654 --> 01:38:30,948
-肯特!——嗨,肯特!
- Kent! - Hey, Kent!

1232
01:38:31,031 --> 01:38:32,992
-肯特!-肯特?
- Kent! - Kent?

1233
01:38:34,910 --> 01:38:37,538
-肯特，你没事吧?-太棒了!
- Kent, you okay? - That was great!

1234
01:38:51,176 --> 01:38:53,596
——收到，一号。-出事了。
- Roger, one. - Something is very wrong.

1235
01:38:54,513 --> 01:38:55,514
出去!
